---
title: Scenario 9 — FullItems Rebound Mid-Animation
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Host as Host View
    participant Box as AnimatedListBox
    participant OldSrc as Old Source Collection
    participant NewSrc as New Source Collection
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Anim as In-Flight Animation

    Note over Box: Transfer animation running\n_pipelineBusy = true\n_inflightCount = 2

    Host->>Box: FullItems = newCollection (binding change)
    Box->>Box: OnFullItemsChanged fires

    Box->>OldSrc: Unsubscribe CollectionChanged
    Note over OldSrc: No more change events from old source

    Box->>Box: SnapAllAnimations()
    Note over Anim: All animations cancelled\ncontainers reset\nghosts removed

    Box->>Pipeline: _pipeline.Clear()\n_batchGeneration++\n_pipelineBusy = false

    Box->>NewSrc: Subscribe CollectionChanged

    Box->>Box: ReplaceVisible(BuildPageSlice(newItems))
    Note over Box: VisibleItems fully replaced\nNo animation — initial population is always instant

    Note over Box: Old source can still fire events\nbut the subscription is gone\n→ they are never received

    Note over Box: New source events will now\nflow through the normal pipeline

    NewSrc-->>Box: CollectionChanged (if new source fires immediately)
    Box->>Pipeline: Classify and enqueue normally

    Note over Box: Result: Clean handover\nOld animations cancelled\nNew source starts fresh
